biotools.summary:
Prediction of Mutation Effects using a Deep Temporal Convolutional Network.

This is the code for the paper Prediction of Mutation Effects using a Deep Temporal Convolutional Network. https://academic.oup.com/bioinformatics/advance-article/doi/10.1093/bioinformatics/btz873/5634146.

The code is compatible with tensorflow-gpu=1.10.0 and python=2.7
